      "description": "Presented in exemplary, showroom-ready condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine cabin appointments, reflects a history of meticulous care and climate-controlled storage. Mechanically indistinguishable from new, this unit offers a rare opportunity for the sophisticated collector or driver who demands nothing short of perfection.",
