    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor? I'm parting with my absolute pride and joy, and it is in incredible, pristine condition! I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, and it\u2019s been kept tucked away in a climate-controlled garage. It drives like a total dream and is seriously spotless inside and out. You honestly won't find one cleaner than this anywhere else. Come take a look and see for yourself\u2014you're going to fall in love the moment you sit behind the wheel!",
      "price": 43500.0,
