    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine Alpine White. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. Mechanically flawless, the VANOS system has been professionally overhauled, and the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced with TMS plates to ensure structural integrity. The limited-slip differential remains tight, providing optimal torque distribution, while the factory-spec suspension maintains its original compliance and turn-in precision. Every bushing is original-equipment grade, and the engine pulls strongly to its 8,000 RPM redline with zero hesitation. This is a collector-quality chassis with a documented service history, free from the common wear patterns of high-mileage units.",
